high_descs: Go to the counter to the right of the sink
Grab the knife off of the counter
Turn right and go to the microwave
Cut the potato in the microwave into two slices
Turn around and go to the sink
Put the knife in the sink
Turn right and go to the microwave
Grab a potato slice out of the microwave
Turn around and go to the sink
Wash the potato in the sink and then take it out
Turn right and go to the microwave
Put the potato in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Putting a clean sliced potato in the microwave

high_descs: Turn to the right, walk forward a few steps, then turn to the left and walk up to the counter space that is to the right of the kitchen sink.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that is lying on the counter.
Turn to the right to face the microwave.
Slice the potato that is in the microwave.
Turn around completely, then to the right to face the kitchen sink.
Place the knife in the kitchen sink.
Turn to the right and go back to the microwave that is on the counter.
Take a slice of potato out of the microwave.
Turn around completely, then to the right to face the sink.
Wash off the potato slice in the kitchen sink before taking it back out.
Turn back to the right and go to the microwave.
Place the slice of potato in the microwave and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean potato slice in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn and go to the counter by the sink.
Pick up a knife on the counter.
Turn and go to the microwave.
Slice the potato in the microwave.
Turn and go to the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn and go to the microwave.
Pick up a slice of potato in the microwave.
Turn and go to the sink.
Wash the slice of potato in the sink.
Turn and go to the microwave.
Put the slice of potato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed slice of potato in the microwave.
